{"tid":1923324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎疫情大爆發　全球迪士尼樂園宣布關閉","createTime":"2020-03-13T04:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T05:44:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbf39e5655d10d99c51695fe1fcc3baa3a0e3c3","tid":1923324,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情全球失控，根據目前最新統計，美國新冠肺炎確診數達1459例、死亡數39例，迪士尼官方宣布，已暫時關閉全球所有的迪士尼遊樂園。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，加州迪士尼樂園表示，雖然樂園內並沒有傳出確診病例，但是為了安全起見，將從本月14日起，關閉遊樂園至3月底。結果經過幾小時後，迪士尼官方又宣布，位在佛羅里達和巴黎的迪士尼樂園，也將自15日起暫時關閉。加上之前上海、香港、日本等國家的迪士尼樂園陸續關閉，全球的6間迪士尼樂園，現在已經因為疫情，全面關閉營業。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/41002</code></pre>"},{"pid":"191ebef01058f070ad7d43233bd7c72e185e6e10","tid":1923324,"uid":205616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:17:09.000Z","msg":"想提醒返個新聞來源係來自同中國統戰部有緊密合作嘅台灣紅媒中時集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247c2b2fe18c1cf4f0072b3f3e4013efce785d6e","tid":1923324,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"191ebef01058f070ad7d43233bd7c72e185e6e10","tid":1923324,"uid":205616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:17:09.000Z","msg":"想提醒返個新聞來源係來自同中國統戰部有緊密合作嘅台灣紅媒中時集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"人民日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4ab4b5b16122f7ef461b048677ab7e2243c19e","tid":1923324,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"奶共敵屎尼"},{"pid":"b83ccfb7ed16cf311f666808bee9595c4a8bee07","tid":1923324,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"23c2e886ee5c536b1a075fb95f9d266da78aa7ce","tid":1923324,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,